headline: Why Dutch Bros is a top stock pick for 2026, while Starbucks lags
summary: Starbucks' (SBUX) ongoing turnaround efforts and Dutch Bros' (BROS) rising popularity are key stories in focus for coffee investors in 2026. Mizuho managing director and senior equity research analyst Nick Setyan explains why Dutch Bros is his top pick in the coffee space and why he has an unfavorable outlook for Starbucks. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Catalysts.
